-- Sony:sees TV unit posting $2.2 billion operating loss in 2011/12
-- 
-- Wed Nov 2, 2011 5:35am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/11/02/us-sony-tv-idUSTRE7A112S20111102

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Sony Corp said on Wednesday it expects its TV unit to post an operating loss of 175 billion yen ($2.2 billion) for the financial year ending in March. 
 The firm said it aims to cut the unit's operating loss by half in the next financial year and return the TV business to profit in the year ending in March 2014. ($1 = 78.280 Japanese Yen) (Reporting by  Isabel Reynolds ; Editing by  Joseph Radford )